{"tid":1384322,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"千奇唔好圍中資公司啊","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:30:26.000Z","uid":239496,"like":84,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e6912bb27876e3d6df43d44257aa794ae06dd117","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:19:00.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢夢到一樣野 <br />\n<br />\n中聯辦重防就個個手足都知 <br />\n但點解都係要去上環呢<br />\n因為個目標係上環 <br />\n所以就要去上環 <br />\n但其實中共其他既國有資產同埋公司一樣都係遍地開花 <br />\n例如中資在港頭5大既中旅社又或者中國銀行咁樣 其實全部都係共產黨 <br />\n如果我地可以將目標定係中資既公司 <br />\n其實咁樣仲安全同埋係全方位抗爭 <br />\nd狗無可能守得晒 全部既中資公司 <br />\n而且影響非常大 <br />\n試諗下 全港中銀或者中旅社比人搞到開唔到門 <br />\n銀行運作唔到 <br />\n中旅社搞唔到大陸團 同批簽証 會有幾大獲 <br />\n<br />\n暴徒千奇唔好圍<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中資公司啊</span></span><br />\n以上係我發夢夢到既野"},{"pid":"9a7f62915154587c4289182a55b82cfda2b81bf6","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:19:11.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"a0260c6eaa31449e448fd4654c83e7296ee3b8e2","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:19:36.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"f93dc3df21961a6159d93982eb19478a970c44de","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"f1cb4e9ea5ffb8e7b41bfad416f6e1dac6675784","tid":1384322,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9ae281436f4b5755f31e4ce905946802ca77e2","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:20:28.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"08d56922f072fd20a09ca47afb38c77a82043503","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:20:53.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"cd34fce7688370fe851e65c5a530af1ebab309f1","tid":1384322,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0