replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:04:53.000Z","msg":"光復"},{"pid":"9b89328a2ae50609886758a61860c15318afe487","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"香港"},{"pid":"e79080669a31c8898e892f61a07c30254d3bbeeb","tid":1384322,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"好驚啊"},{"pid":"5b72b05a7e7fd73a1beebc40701fc9971052df91","tid":1384322,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"講起中資公司<br />\n唔知點解佢地門口咁乾淨<br />\n明明垃圾公司<br />\n應該堆滿垃圾先襯佢地"},{"pid":"ed00481c852218754df9d0bac02331f959ff2301","tid":1384322,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:08:00.000Z","msg":"[停止爭論] 無論政府成唔成立獨立調查委員會 我地都應該不斷抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsCbBT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsCbBT</a>"},{"pid":"defd259abb5dcb1361c197d8d8763858b87122f5","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"時代"},{"pid":"819f3bc78096c25545ac572845edfe02a62dd356","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"革命"},{"pid":"3890b3d43ff5345985f58e20b18ab35af01314d9","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">釋放梁天琦</span></span>"},{"pid":"e9437aa9e0319fd23b412271b9b07c420053831a","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"光復"},{"pid":"9a2baf5d7c4aa0cd2d437eb6c5cdf369159ba035","tid":1384322,"uid":70332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"可試"},{"pid":"92ed9fcfc4816ea935b5b4335fbb207496aed599","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"香港"},{"pid":"d31522e3e19aa6fab815dbca8ef660eef369cebb","tid":1384322,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"華潤大廈（英語：China Resources Building），為香港的一座甲級寫字樓，位處香港灣仔港灣道26號，於1983年落成。華潤大廈由兩座分別為50層178米高的主樓及及25層高的副樓組成，另設3層地庫停車場，其中地下至2樓為商場，主樓3至5樓為中國外交部駐香港簽證辦事處，副樓3樓以上為香港瑞吉酒店，主樓其餘為寫字樓部分。[1]<br />\n<br />\n華潤大廈除與深圳中國華潤大廈及華潤金融大廈共同構成華潤集團總部外，華潤附屬公司的辦事處亦設在此，包括華潤置地（46樓）、華潤水泥（44樓）、華潤醫療集團（41樓4101-03室）、華潤創業有限公司（39樓）、華潤金融（37樓）、華潤電力（20樓2001－2002室，同時設總部於中國華潤大廈）、華潤物業有限公司（12樓）及華潤五豐（8樓，已遷），其他租戶還包括西藏水資源（34樓3401室，已遷往黃竹坑）、中策集團（32樓3206 - 3210室）、京華山一（11樓）及獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會（IPCC）（10樓1006至1010室）等。"},{"pid":"fc99cd5abaff45475008fe66a4f5a9dbed53bfad","tid":1384322,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"中資非華潤莫屬"},{"pid":"c803928e45ee1d7d2fd85850525586b2344b807a","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d31522e3e19aa6fab815dbca8ef660eef369cebb","tid":1384322,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"華潤大廈（英語：China Resources Building），為香港的一座甲級寫字樓，位處香港灣仔港灣道26號，於1983年落成。華潤大廈由兩座分別為50層178米高的主樓及及25層高的副樓組成，另設3層地庫停車場，其中地下至2樓為商場，主樓3至5樓為中國外交部駐香港簽證辦事處，副樓3樓以上為香港瑞吉酒店，主樓其餘為寫字樓部分。[1]<br />\n<br />\n華潤大廈除與深圳中國華潤大廈及華潤金融大廈共同構成華潤集團總部外，華潤附屬公司的辦事處亦設在此，包括華潤置地（46樓）、華潤水泥（44樓）、華潤醫療集團（41樓4101-03室）、華潤創業有限公司（39樓）、華潤金融（37樓）、華潤電力（20樓2001－2002室，同時設總部於中國華潤大廈）、華潤物業有限公司（12樓）及華潤五豐（8樓，已遷），其他租戶還包括西藏水資源（34樓3401室，已遷往黃竹坑）、中策集團（32樓3206 - 3210室）、京華山一（11樓）及獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會（IPCC）（10樓1006至1010室）等。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"華潤堂、華潤萬家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d44f4cb9e7e258318f388b9f1b3208436ab803","tid":1384322,"uid":269285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fef4f59e3ab88b92cf0679f440ae7364c44116bc","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e66de542b07e13cace946367d65d7b2f894d3170","tid":1384322,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"059fe220fa127d2af51611c214393eac4b10643a","tid":1384322,"uid":132770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"尤其是華潤大厦<br />\n真係唔好搞"},{"pid":"0622f5226d13cd701808a18a0a02ec3491fb903c","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d063b519181357cf93e85e15b452c4f205dc8a47","tid":1384322,"uid":244607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a01e5a1e698eb688db44224ae2c462414f20c79","tid":1384322,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593479a56498fd1ddbe5ffd284ebf41caa03fdd9","tid":1384322,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:13:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2cba611824f96303950aaf89e56ac39abd1530b1","tid":1384322,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"反紅打黑  遍地開花<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi